Mauritania Grants Exploration Licenses for Uranium, Gold, Iron

-- B y   O u d a a   M a r o u f
-- 
2011-04-23T08:47:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-23/mauritania-grants-exploration-licenses-for-uranium-gold-iron.html
Mauritania granted two uranium
exploration licenses to Lusitania Uranium Mauritania in the Rjem
and Oued Kharroub South areas, said AMI, the state news agency.  Two more uranium licenses were awarded to Agrineq SA and
Mauritania Resources Ltd. in Aguelt East and North Bir Ould Ben
Nasser areas, AMI said, citing a Council of Ministers statement
after its weekly meeting April 21 in Nouakchott, the capital.  The government also granted two gold-exploration licenses
to Mauritania for Mining & Services in the Bou Chamada and
Adekmar areas, one iron-exploration license to Wadi Al Rawda
Industrial Investments LLC in El Batha and one quartz license to
Mauritanian Minerals Company SA in Oued Teguid√©.  To contact the reporter on this story:  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
